#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:1
msgid "Features Overview"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:3
msgid ""
"The CPRMV API delivers five core capabilities derived directly from the "
"`serve_api/src/serve.py` implementation and the `data/cprmvmethods.ttl` "
"methods registry."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:7
msgid "On-the-fly rule retrieval"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:9
msgid ""
"Rules are resolved and fetched live from official publication repositories — "
"nothing is pre-loaded or cached between requests. When a request arrives:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:11
msgid ""
"The rule set identifier is parsed to detect which publication method applies "
"(BWB, CVDR, CELLAR, or DMN 1.3)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:12
msgid ""
"The publication URL is constructed using the format templates in "
"`cprmvmethods.ttl`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:13
msgid "The XML publication is downloaded via HTTPS."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:14
msgid "An XSLT stylesheet transforms it to CPRMV Turtle."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:15
msgid "rdflib navigates the resulting RDF graph to the requested rule."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:17
msgid ""
"This means the API always serves the authoritative source — no "
"synchronisation or stale data."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:21
msgid "Multi-repository support"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cfeatures%5Coverview.md:23
msgid ""
